{# NOVA — Our Story + stats. #}
<section class="nova-section nova-divider">
  <div class="max-w-[1400px] mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
      <div data-aos="fade-right">
        <p class="text-nova-mid text-[11px] tracking-[0.4em] uppercase mb-3">Our Story</p>
        <h2 class="section-heading text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-8">Built on a Simple Idea</h2>
        <p class="text-nova-light text-base leading-relaxed mb-6 font-light">We didn't start NOVA to sell sunglasses. We started it because we couldn't find eyewear that actually did something for our health.</p>
        <p class="text-nova-mid text-base leading-relaxed mb-6 font-light">Screens give us headaches. Artificial light ruins our sleep. UV damages our eyes silently. The solutions existed — but nobody was putting them together in one clean product.</p>
        <p class="text-nova-mid text-base leading-relaxed mb-10 font-light">So we made three lenses. Each with a clear purpose. No trends, no hype — just eyewear that works.</p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-8 border-t border-white/[0.06] pt-8">
          <div><p class="text-2xl font-bold">3</p><p class="text-nova-mid text-[11px] tracking-[0.15em] uppercase mt-1">Products</p></div>
          <div><p class="text-2xl font-bold">100%</p><p class="text-nova-mid text-[11px] tracking-[0.15em] uppercase mt-1">UV Blocking</p></div>
          <div><p class="text-2xl font-bold">1</p><p class="text-nova-mid text-[11px] tracking-[0.15em] uppercase mt-1">Mission</p></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="relative" data-aos="fade-left">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <div class="aspect-[3/4] bg-nova-charcoal overflow-hidden"><img src="{{ 'images/nova/day-side.webp' | asset }}" alt="" class="w-full h-full object-contain p-6" /></div>
          <div class="aspect-[3/4] bg-nova-charcoal overflow-hidden mt-8"><img src="{{ 'images/nova/night-front.webp' | asset }}" alt="" class="w-full h-full object-contain p-6" /></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
